        {"id":1,"type":"paragraph","text":"個人事業・小さなお店のためのオンラインサポート","style":{"align":"center","backgroundColor":"#eef2ff","textColor":"#4338ca","padding":12,"width":"full","fontSize":14,"fontWeight":"500","underline":false}},
        {"id":2,"type":"heading","text":"Studio Note","style":{"align":"center","backgroundColor":"#ffffff","textColor":"#3730a3","padding":20,"width":"full","fontSize":42,"fontWeight":"700","underline":false}},
        {"id":3,"type":"heading","text":"伝えたいことを整理して、\n続けられる形に整えます。","style":{"align":"center","backgroundColor":"#ffffff","textColor":"#1e293b","padding":12,"width":"full","fontSize":30,"fontWeight":"700","underline":false}},
        {"id":4,"type":"paragraph","text":"Webページの更新、資料づくり、日々の事務作業。\nひとりでは後回しになりやすい仕事を、必要な分だけお手伝いする架空の個人サービスです。","style":{"align":"center","backgroundColor":"#ffffff","textColor":"#475569","padding":16,"width":"full","fontSize":17,"fontWeight":"normal","underline":false}},
        {"id":5,"type":"button","text":"サービスについて相談する","style":{"align":"center","backgroundColor":"#ffffff","textColor":"#ffffff","padding":18,"width":"full","fontSize":16,"fontWeight":"700","underline":false},"link":{"type":"custom","pageId":null,"customUrl":"#"}},
        {"id":6,"type":"divider","text":"","style":{"align":"left","backgroundColor":"#ffffff","textColor":"#334155","padding":16,"width":"full","fontSize":16,"fontWeight":"normal","underline":false}},
        {"id":7,"type":"heading","text":"こんなお悩みはありませんか？","style":{"align":"center","backgroundColor":"#ffffff","textColor":"#1e293b","padding":20,"width":"full","fontSize":28,"fontWeight":"700","underline":false}},
        {"id":8,"type":"paragraph","text":"Web更新が止まりがち\n\nお知らせやサービス内容を更新したいのに、日々の仕事で後回しになっている。","style":{"align":"left","backgroundColor":"#f8fafc","textColor":"#334155","padding":24,"width":"third","fontSize":15,"fontWeight":"500","underline":false}},
        {"id":9,"type":"paragraph","text":"資料がまとまらない\n\n伝えたい内容はあるけれど、文章や構成を整理するところで手が止まってしまう。","style":{"align":"left","backgroundColor":"#f8fafc","textColor":"#334155","padding":24,"width":"third","fontSize":15,"fontWeight":"500","underline":false}},
        {"id":10,"type":"paragraph","text":"細かな作業に追われる\n\n入力や整形などの小さな作業が積み重なり、本来の仕事に集中しにくい。","style":{"align":"left","backgroundColor":"#f8fafc","textColor":"#334155","padding":24,"width":"third","fontSize":15,"fontWeight":"500","underline":false}},
        {"id":11,"type":"heading","text":"提供できること","style":{"align":"center","backgroundColor":"#ffffff","textColor":"#1e293b","padding":24,"width":"full","fontSize":28,"fontWeight":"700","underline":false}},
        {"id":12,"type":"paragraph","text":"Web・情報整理サポート\n\n・簡単なページ更新\n・掲載文章の整理\n・お知らせやFAQの下書き\n・HTMLデータの整形","style":{"align":"left","backgroundColor":"#eef2ff","textColor":"#312e81","padding":28,"width":"half","fontSize":16,"fontWeight":"500","underline":false}},
        {"id":13,"type":"paragraph","text":"事務・資料サポート\n\n・表や文章の整形\n・定型作業の手順整理\n・資料のたたき台作成\n・小さな業務改善の相談","style":{"align":"left","backgroundColor":"#faf5ff","textColor":"#581c87","padding":28,"width":"half","fontSize":16,"fontWeight":"500","underline":false}},
        {"id":14,"type":"heading","text":"ご依頼の流れ","style":{"align":"center","backgroundColor":"#ffffff","textColor":"#1e293b","padding":24,"width":"full","fontSize":28,"fontWeight":"700","underline":false}},
        {"id":15,"type":"paragraph","text":"01　相談\n困っていることと、希望する期限を伺います。","style":{"align":"center","backgroundColor":"#ffffff","textColor":"#1e293b","padding":22,"width":"third","fontSize":15,"fontWeight":"500","underline":false}},
        {"id":16,"type":"paragraph","text":"02　提案\n作業範囲、進め方、スケジュールをご案内します。","style":{"align":"center","backgroundColor":"#ffffff","textColor":"#1e293b","padding":22,"width":"third","fontSize":15,"fontWeight":"500","underline":false}},
        {"id":17,"type":"paragraph","text":"03　作業・確認\n途中経過を共有しながら、確認後に納品します。","style":{"align":"center","backgroundColor":"#ffffff","textColor":"#1e293b","padding":22,"width":"third","fontSize":15,"fontWeight":"500","underline":false}},
        {"id":18,"type":"paragraph","text":"まずは、小さな困りごとから。\n\n「何を頼めるか分からない」という段階でも大丈夫です。\n現在の状況を伺い、無理のない進め方を一緒に考えます。","style":{"align":"center","backgroundColor":"#312e81","textColor":"#ffffff","padding":36,"width":"full","fontSize":18,"fontWeight":"500","underline":false}},
        {"id":19,"type":"button","text":"相談内容をまとめてみる","style":{"align":"center","backgroundColor":"#312e81","textColor":"#ffffff","padding":22,"width":"full","fontSize":16,"fontWeight":"700","underline":false},"link":{"type":"custom","pageId":null,"customUrl":"#"}},
        {"id":20,"type":"paragraph","text":"Studio Note\n架空の個人サービス紹介サイト作成例","style":{"align":"center","backgroundColor":"#0f172a","textColor":"#cbd5e1","padding":24,"width":"full","fontSize":13,"fontWeight":"normal","underline":false}}
